propertyModel.name: Property identifier name. Information is required.
propertyModel.label: Property displayed label. Information is required.
propertyModel.sortIndex: The order in which the property will be displayed in workpack. Information is required.
propertyModel.precision: The number of decimal places to be used in property values. Default value is zero.
propertyModel.possibleValues: List of options will be displayed to select in the property value. Information is required.
propertyModel.domain: Domain to list the localities. Information is required.
propertyModel.sector: Sector to filter the organizations will be displayed in option list of property value. Information is required.
propertyModel.defaultValue: Default value will be inputed in property value.
propertyModel.fullLine: Indicate the property width. When it is checked, the property will be displayed occupay the entire width of the screen.
propertyModel.required: The property value information is required.
propertyModel.multiSelection: If it is checked, will be selected more then one option to property value.
propertyModel.rows: Number of lines do textarea property.
propertyModel.helpText: Help text to be displayed in property.

organization.sector: Sector of activity of the organization. The selection of one option is required.
organization.businessName: Organization name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
organization.socialName: Organization social name. Information is required.
organization.address: Organization complete address. Information is not required.
organization.phoneNumber: Organization phone number. Enter the phone number with area code. Only numbers. Information is not required.
organization.contactEmail: Organization contact e-mail. Enter a valid e-mail. Information is not required.
organization.website: Organization Website. Information is not required.

domain.name: Domain name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
domain.rootLocalityName: Root locality name. Information is required.
domain.rootLocalitFullName: Root locality fullname. Information is required.
domain.rootLocalityLatitude: Root locality GPS latitude. Information is not required.
domain.rootLocalityLongitude: Root locality GPS longitude. Information is not required.

locality.name: Locality name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
locality.localityLatitude: Locality GPS latitude. Information is not required.
locality.localityLongitude: Locality GPS longitude. Information is not required.

measureUnit.name: Meansure unit name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
measureUnit.fullName: Meansure unit fullname. Information is required.
measureUnit.precision: Precision to be used in the decimal places of the values. Default value is zero. Information is required.

permission.level: Permission level. Read for only visualization, edit for changes and none for no permission.

planModel.name: Plan model name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
planModel.fullName: Plan model fullname. Information is required.
planModel.sharedWith: Offices with which you wish to share this plan model. Select the option 'All' to sharing with all offices. Information is not required.

workpackModel.modelName: Workpack model name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
workpackModel.modelNameInPlural: Workpack model name in plural. Information is required.
workpackModel.position: Position of workpack model tab or panel in worpack view. Default value is the next position after the last used by models in the same level. Information is required.
workpackModel.icon: Icon to be showed in the workpack card. Default value is defined by workpack model type. Information is required.
workpackModel.sortedBy: The property will be used to order the workpacks created from this workpack model. Default value is the property 'name'. Information is required.
workpackModel.dashboardShowStakeholders: Roles by stakeholders should be displaed in workpack dashboard. Default values are possible roles from stakeholder section. Information is not required.
workpackModel.stakeholdersPossibleRolesPerson: Possible roles of a stakeholder person in workpack stakeholder section. Default values are selected when the model is created. Information required if the stakeholder section is on.
workpackModel.stakeholdersPossibleRolesOrganization: Possible roles of a stakeholder organization in workpack stakeholder section. Default values are selected when the model is created. Information required if the stakeholder section is on.

reportModel.name: Report model name. Information is required.
reportModel.preferredFormat: Preferred format file to export report. Default value is 'PDF'. Information is required.
reportModel.fullName: Report model fullname. Information is required.

office.name: Office name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.

plan.planModelName: Name of the plan model linked to the plan. This information is readonly.
plan.name: Plan name. Maximum size 25 characters. Information is required.
plan.start: Plan date start. It should be before plan finish date. Information is required.
plan.finish: Plan date finish. It should be after plan start date. Information is required.

person.address: Person full address. Information is not required.
person.phoneNumber: Person phone number. Enter the phone number with area code. Only numbers. Information is not required.

person.howDoYouWantYourNameDisplayed: Input your nickname or how you want your name to be displayed.
